Metadata: University of California Sea Grant Cooperative Extension

Tidelines will be published quarterly as a local newsletter dealing with practical problems in the areas of Commercial and sport fisheries; Seafood processing, aquaculture, marine education and youth programs, marine research, waterfront management, boating industry, marine transportation, environmental policy, and coastal engineering. Cover articles include: From coastal conflict to win-win, Clean, cook, can tuna; Frozen storage wraps for tuna.
